SKELLIG ISLAND saved ground off the early pace, was under a ride leaving the far turn, stayed inside into the lane but came up empty. GRAND KINGDOM eased back from between runners nearing the first turn, dropped in then lacked a rally. DANCING MISCHIEF , three wide stalking the pace, moved up between runners near the half, could not keep pace while under asking past the five sixteenths and tired. TROPANDHAGEN cleared early, set the pace towards the inside, moved away mid way through the backstretch run, was engaged past the five sixteenths, battled to upper stretch then faltered through the final furlong. ELEVATED GAME broke sluggishly, was used four wide to reach a forward spot into the far turn, chased outside rivals into the far turn then faltered.

RACE.FOOTNOTES: ENERGY EFFICIENT stalked the pace outside horses, advanced four deep leaving the turn, took command turning for home and drew away. MONEY ROOM , in the two path behind horses on the turn, moved to the four path at the head of the stretch and rallied. MARGIE'S FUN SON , steadied in traffic about a furlong after the break, saved ground on the turn, advanced along the inner rail to mid stretch and flattened out. INFINITE SERIES , rank leaving the backstretch, was fanned six deep leaving the turn and rallied. BY HAND , under urging early, gained the lead along the inner rail entering the turn, lost the advantage in upper stretch and gave way. CATCHING STARS , unhurried down the backstretch, raced along the inner rail and lacked room through most of the stretch. LORD OF MISCHIEF prompted the pace in the two path between horses and weakened. MIDNIGHT MINE stumbled leaving the starting gate, was fanned seven wide turning for home and failed to be a factor. JOHN JAY showed speed three wide, drifted to the five path turning for home, faltered and was eased.
